data.title: Beaufontaine Subdivision Homes for Sale in Heber City Utah
data.meta_description: 5 New listed new contraction homes for sale in wonderful Heber City neighborhood. Home for sale priced from the low $300,000 with several options & floor plans to select from. Search all homes for sale in Heber City fast & easy.
data.text:
Beaufontaine Neighborhood Homes for Sale in Heber City

Beaufontaine is a newer construction subdivision of custom & semi-custom home being built in a central Heber City neighborhood. Most lots are over one acre and the setting need to be seen to be appreciated. Located in a rural yet convenient location just minutes to main street.

Homes in Beaufontaine start in the high $700,000's but for the location, quality and large lots they are really a good value for the area.

For questions or to schedule a showing of one of Beaufontaine neighborhood homes please call Scott Rozier 385-296-4321.
